Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  该起床了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八  八点！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟…迟到了迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这么着急呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:00:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  看错时间了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是高中生了～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺你入学～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定来网球部看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定来柔道部看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定来茶道部看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定来珠算部看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  你在嘟哝什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  和和  其实我在想该加入什么社团好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你还没决定吗  已经开学两周了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是可是…我是个运动白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化系的社团也不是很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去就会变成家里蹲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不参加社团活动就变家里蹲了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想想  唯从来没有参加过社团活动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}家…家…里…蹲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扑哧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然觉得必须要做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但到底做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去社团参观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团参观？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部啊  轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:05:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我准备进文学部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:05:00.21,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日文中「文芸」是中文里「文学」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入部申请书都写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你在做什么啊  律
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧  快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 废部了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确来说是即将废部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前年那届的部员全都毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这个月里没有四人入部的话  就要废部了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…难怪音乐室里一个人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉  我等会还有音乐课
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个漂亮的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是在说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把这些资料发给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:05:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯着看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟不上调子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨手笨脚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然呆…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废部就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去文学部了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在一个人都没有就意味着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我入部了就是部长了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  刚才谈到的那个轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写成「轻松的音乐」的「轻音」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻松的音乐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  轻松的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待入部志愿者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个～我想参观一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参观轻音部？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是合唱部…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加入轻音部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  是合唱部…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在部员很少  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  绝对不会让你失望的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么强行招人会让人家为难的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的约定…难道是骗人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鼓手  澪是贝司手…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…一直组乐队…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是约好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们一起去看演唱会的那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时你说的话难道是骗人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那回想是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个了  来组乐队吧乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是律在自说自话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪不是也说过要组吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  发展为职业级以后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出费就是三七开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别瞎编了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我只会键盘乐器  但如果不嫌弃的话就请让我加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万分感谢  这样只要再有一个人加入就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…已经把我算进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是琴吹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鼓手田井中律
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是负责贝司的秋山澪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…还有就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉他手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然进了高中  总想做点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那就做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道该做什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要加一份薯条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是第一次来快餐店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直希望被人问一次「还要加一份薯条吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉  请开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  为了在这个月再找到一个部员  开始作战会议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是接下去要想的～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在入部的话  会得到很特别的特典之类啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特典…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  要是会得到什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说汽车啊  别墅什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是很厉害…但是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是请吃冰淇淋啦  帮忙做作业之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有人为这个入部吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  怎么做才好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己都觉得无聊了怎么行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那想点什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  总之先…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:11:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月已经  只剩下…一周了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…谁也没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没组成乐队就直接废部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那绝对不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻…音乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯做得真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我决定加入轻音乐部了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里都做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过既然叫「轻」音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定都是些简单的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口笛之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种没干劲的社团算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  好像要组乐团哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我不会弹吉他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你会弹些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响板…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…很适合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人打算加入了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  这套茶具虽然很漂亮  不过喝完后记得要收拾好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！这下不用废部了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平泽 唯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看名字好像很厉害耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是吉他手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒啦！强力团员加入啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部…轻音部…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不从这里过去  就到不了轻音部…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音乐部在音乐教室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然才刚进来  难以启齿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是得说我不加入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…轻音部里都有些怎样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？不干啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说不干就不干吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不…不不不…不不不不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟不上调子又笨手笨脚的天然呆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你就是那个平泽唯同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你打算加入啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思误会你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弹吉他超厉害的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都在等你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像误会了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家～新部员来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎加入轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热烈欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  准备上茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不提走人的事情好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平泽同学想演奏怎样的音乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢怎样的乐队？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的吉他手呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是得说出来  其实我根本不会弹什么吉他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其…其…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉米·亨德雷斯（Jimi Hendrix）？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…吉…吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉米·佩奇（Jimmy Page）？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰夫·贝克（Jeff Beck）？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道有很多吉他手都是J开头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊！是杰夫·贝克啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说摇滚吉他手只有两种  杰夫·贝克和杰夫·贝克以外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远在追求新鲜音感  极富挑战的吉他手！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很专业啊  平泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平泽同学这样的人能加入真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们一星期内不能再找不到一个人加入的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要被废部了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的谢谢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下越来越说不出口了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不讲清楚又不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…真的很抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上我是想来说我不打算加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不会弹吉他  本以为是演奏别的乐器…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你会什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响…口琴！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  口琴这里有哦  吹吹看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我不会吹！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  既然打算加入我们社团  说明你还是对音乐感兴趣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其它想参加的社团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么特别想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴边的鸭子怎么能让她飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了免于被废部！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要劝她回头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再添一杯茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有饼干和松糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下饵了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起！本来不想吃你们这么多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我们每天这样一起吃点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么觉得偏离主题了…好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平泽同学  你还有什么其它喜欢的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的东西我都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…就惦记着吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常放假你在家都怎么过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闲呆着…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢什么东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的东西…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太热太冷我都不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天都窝在桌炉里面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就趴在地板上无所事事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棘手…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…那我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  别走！求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要在这里闲呆着就好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去拿些好吃的点心来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…随随便便就交上申请书…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还让你们这么期待…我该怎样道歉才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才应该道歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  强留你下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  至少听听我们的演奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我演奏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One  Two  Three  Four
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢…我觉得很难用语言表达…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很精彩呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好直接！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过感觉很有趣的样子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加入这个社团！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么作为轻音部活动开始纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我的相机…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  可我完全不会乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  当经纪人怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  这又不是运动部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  就借此机会开始学吉他怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这个好像很难…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦  我们知道的都会教你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听过刚才的演奏  我有种我也可以做到的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  最后你还是加入了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她们一定要我加入嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是做经纪人什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被别人这么说感觉真不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是作为正式成员加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们说会从头教我弹吉他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那么说你要买把新吉他了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…不知道会不会借我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5000日元左右应该能买到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓这孩子去做部员能行吗…轻音部！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.09,0:23:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这三位就是轻音部的伙伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.32,0:23:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和这些可遇不可求的愉快的人成为伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.75,0:23:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯…唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.42,0:23:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:23:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大家
